code: /**  * All other methods like nextInt()/nextDouble()... depends on this, so we just need to overwrite  * this.  *  * @param bits Random bits  * @return The next pseudorandom value from this random number  * generator's sequence  */ @Override public int next(int bits) {     long nextSeed = seed ^ (seed << 21).     nextSeed ^= (nextSeed >>> 35).     nextSeed ^= (nextSeed << 4).     seed = nextSeed.     return (int) (nextSeed & ((1L << bits) - 1)). }
